## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/imutcontainerinfo">ImutContainerInfo</a> - Specialization for pointer values to treat pointers as references to unique objects.

Pointers are thus compared by their addresses.

Definition at line 934 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/adt/immutableset-h">ImmutableSet.h</a>.
